<p> One of the goals of the 1st stage of Zhong Yuan Qigong is to open energy channels. Therefore, before starting any exercises as well as in the morning and at night - after sleeping and before going to bed - it is necessary to open the channels on the arms and legs. </P>
<p> In the human body there are 12 major energy channels connecting the internal organs with the surface of the body. The initial and final portions of these channels pass along the side surfaces of the fingers and toes, and the initial and final points of these channels are located in the corners of the nails. </P>
<p> When performing this exercise, you need to be aware that you are opening these channels, clearing contaminated areas,”‘squeezing” a stagnant and thickened “something".